data.description: Escape to your dream ranch-style home on a generous 2.51-acre plot, featuring three cozy bedrooms, two well-fitted bathrooms, and a handy office space. The heart of the house is an open-plan layout, connecting a modern kitchen to the inviting living and dining areas. Unleash your creativity with a spacious unfinished basement, perfect for a home gym or additional living space. With a convenient three-car garage, parking and storage are a breeze. The vast outdoors provides room for play, gardening, or simply enjoying the tranquility of your own rural retreat. This property offers a harmonious blend of comfort and space, inviting you to create lasting memories in your ideal home.
